node.text:
Hey babies I hope you enjoy this dewy glowy summer look! I had a lot of fun making it for you and have listed all products below.💗
-Primer : @urbandecaycosmetics 
-Brow Pencil : @anastasiabeverlyhills 
-Brow Shadow : @maccosmetics 
-Brow Gel : @anastasiabeverlyhills 
-Tinted moisturizer : @yslbeauty 
-Eyeshadow Pallete : @amrezy x @anastasiabeverlyhills 
-Eyeshadow : @maccosmetics 
-Concealer : @yslbeauty 
-Cream Bronzer : @chanel.beauty 
-Cream Blush : @chanel.beauty 
-Translucent Powder : @lauramercier 
-Lashes : @lashinktampa 
-Mascara : @lancomeofficial 
-Setting Spray : @tatcha
-Lip Liner : @maccosmetics 
-Lip Gloss : @fentybeauty

node.text: You’re 3 now and I still can’t believe how fast time goes by! It’s almost impossible to imagine what life was like before you because somehow you were always there. It’s like you were just waiting to come into this world when you were supposed to. I’m so grateful I get to share this journey with you and for every day I get to be your mama! Here’s to life and here’s to you my beautiful baby bean!😍🙏🏽💗

node.text: Happy 2nd Birthday baby! I can’t believe you’re already 2 I wish you would slow down a little! Me and your father love you soooo much and are so so proud of you! This past year you took your first steps and are now saying full sentences. What amazes me the most about you is your kind heart and how you say hi to everyone you meet. You also hug and kiss the other kids at daycare when they cry because they miss their parents. How are you so brave already!? I just want you to know that I love you more then myself and am so grateful to be your mother!😭🙏🏽💗
